South African cricket coach, Mark Boucher, says he had the coronavirus and did not know it. Phill Magakoe / AFP JOHANNESBURG - Cricket South Africa withdraws disciplinary charges against Mark Boucher. WATCH: CSA speaks out on Boucher, Smith CSA concludes that there is no basis to sustain racism charges against Boucher. The charges relate to the alleged use of a vulgar word against former teammate Paul Adams. 